{"id": 2845, "genre": 1001, "title": "如果时光机能穿梭过去，你对 10 年前的自己有什么人生建议？", "description": "啊，多啦A梦真的你来啦！（题图来自：iStock ©️ sorbetto ）", "record_count": 3214, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190314135743Myl0T8EwLUekjxcI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-20T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 334336, "content": "重新填高考志愿", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614321}, {"id": 334337, "content": "攒劲学英语，用Coursera体验大学学科，gap一年去实习，然后申请国外大学 （致十年前在准备高考的我）", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285506}, {"id": 336897, "content": "好好学英语", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578448}, {"id": 334338, "content": "倾家荡产买比特币", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612542}, {"id": 340226, "content": "买房去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641556}, {"id": 334339, "content": "不要sy了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 334340, "content": "重视你每一次直觉上的犹豫和怀疑，因为那个可能是真正的你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428507}, {"id": 335108, "content": "，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616462}, {"id": 334341, "content": "好好学习啊，考个好大学，再谈个恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390776}, {"id": 334853, "content": "更积极的交些朋友，多看书，多关心别人的感受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615519}, {"id": 335109, "content": "做真实的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616462}, {"id": 337925, "content": "去学会做人吧不要问为什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631103}, {"id": 335366, "content": "别只知道学习，去打架。别故意孤僻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1183554}, {"id": 345606, "content": "自信一点，做人有原则一点，做人纹理一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063467}, {"id": 334343, "content": "早睡早起，不熬夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614332}, {"id": 335111, "content": "听妈妈的话，多做运动多喝牛奶早睡\n这样我就不用那么矮", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616465}, {"id": 343815, "content": "好好学习，坚持看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508716}, {"id": 334344, "content": "及时止损", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586632}, {"id": 334345, "content": "如果每个人穿越回去都说要趁早买房，那么买不起的仍然是那些人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807000}, {"id": 335369, "content": "不说了\n自己开开心心地过吧\n十年前我7岁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331452}, {"id": 334346, "content": "好好学习，争取上985", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964216}, {"id": 334347, "content": "好好学习呀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588365}, {"id": 334348, "content": "千金难买早知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378846}, {"id": 334860, "content": "睡觉 吃好 现在就能好十倍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163079}, {"id": 335116, "content": "好好玩好好睡，学习这种事中学再努力也不急∠( ᐛ 」∠)＿\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616487}, {"id": 334349, "content": "努力工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614343}, {"id": 335117, "content": "好好学习😭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613516}, {"id": 336654, "content": "多思考，多看书，多自律", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462562}, {"id": 334352, "content": "保护眼睛。。多喝牛奶。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511306}, {"id": 334353, "content": "十年前我才十岁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462053}, {"id": 334354, "content": "早些画画，努力画画", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156862}, {"id": 334355, "content": "不要宅，多出去走走，说不定就有女朋友了。", "image": "img/option/option/20190320180604oepMCStIcvsrxEB6", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226893}, {"id": 335891, "content": "多懂事，理解家人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520615}, {"id": 334356, "content": "少吃点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540821}, {"id": 334357, "content": "好好学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607991}, {"id": 336661, "content": "小学毕业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623462}, {"id": 339221, "content": "别太在意别人说的话，活的潇洒些。可十年前我才4岁，说了这些她也不懂吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637638}, {"id": 334358, "content": "好好学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614362}, {"id": 335126, "content": "放她走吧，你不爱她", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678744}, {"id": 336150, "content": "买房", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619261}, {"id": 334359, "content": "学门技术", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1584909}, {"id": 334360, "content": "我想自己会被自己打死，因为人最恨剧透！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609201}, {"id": 335128, "content": "有点自信，怀点希望", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806190}, {"id": 334361, "content": "好好读书 要自信", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614365}, {"id": 335130, "content": "对自己要有自信，好好学习，不要认识没有必要的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616542}, {"id": 334363, "content": "开始健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614369}, {"id": 334875, "content": "选择你心中的那个学校，那个专业吧！不要整天只知道玩玩玩！多看点书，多学点知识，多认识点人，多开拓下眼界！独立一点，不要被父母几句话忽悠的找不到方向了！注意市场动向！与时俱进！不要整天守着自己一亩三分地！多出去看看！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604407}, {"id": 335132, "content": "告诉自己未来是要考研的\n告诉他别在碰彩票", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616596}, {"id": 334365, "content": "好好度过美好的童年！勇于探索未来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614371}, {"id": 335133, "content": "别吃冷的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1562683}]}